==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Organicism
<hw>Or*gan"i*cism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>The doctrine of the localization of disease, or which refers it
always to a material lesion of an organ.</def>
<rj><au>Dunglison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

